me": "screenshot-bully2 (1).png", "id": "3109815769292844", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982563_3109815772626177_6284524619823654227_n.png?_nc_cat=110&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=MFHDl4IDNwIQ7kNvgEGa_8M&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYB0OYPhbZuAsocSVR8Cjx7U0v4f60sUX54Mj3U_DhfiKQ&oe=66CDC09A"}, {"file_name": "screenshot-bully3.png", "id": "732978577649854", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982492_732978580983187_8954213730478558859_n.png?_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=xqYM1n11PZUQ7kNvgE522QR&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDxvhXJA8b77Wyvjjz-Ey5cSwi-73J1zdK-1wio9b493w&oe=66CDCEC4"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "Ultrasclash V", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Ultrasclash V is a unique blend of three of the most beloved gaming concepts: anime, fighting, and sandbox approach. Combined, they create a fast paced, high octane virtual reality experience, in which you fight hordes of hostile cacti-men in a desperate, yet unmistakably hilarious, fight for survival.\n\nFEATURES\n\nPunch Movement System: we created a VR locomotion system which allows you to roam the map using your fists, punching in the direction you choose to move to!\n\nCrazy Bullet Time fights: just like in The Matrix, freeze time to gain a tactical advantage and defeat your opponents.\n\nPhysical engine: we bring you accurate physics feedbacks in addition to badass sounds and enemies, all reacting realistically to your punches.\n\nAwesome cartoonish stylized graphics!!!", "short_description": "Ultras Fighter is a sandbox anime fighting game, designed and primed to bring you a unique and creative approach to being a hero, just like in your favourite anime!"}]}, "developer_name": "IOX S.r.l.", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.ultrasclash.com/3009-2/", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://www.ultrasclash.com/terms-of-service/", "publisher_name": "IOX S.r.l.", "support_we